<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Solen</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-29 16:26:02</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Lt. Mdriam does indeed drop this item as well as the granite earing.  I wore this piece up until I got my sheer bone mask, and have passed it on to a low level guildmate.<BR>
<BR>
It's been a while since I've seen him in NK.  Saw him a total of 2 times.  Dropped the Specs the first time, the earring the second.<BR>
<BR>
I have a screenshot of the specs and had submitted it to Eq'Lizer (http://gameznet.com/eq/) so go there to see that it is indeed not a fake.  However it may have been removed from the drop list, since I know of no one else that has ever gotten one.<BR>
<BR>
Midriam is a Guard, so I do believe you'll take a hit agains the Qeynos guards if you kill him. Cant remember for sure...it's been a long time.</font></td></tr></table>
