<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have seen Lt. Midraim twice.  The first time he was just South of the Wood bridge and was killed by a griffawn before I could do anything.  The Second time I saw him a little NW of gypsies again fighting a griffawn.  I helped him finish the griffawn off or it would have surely killed him.  I put him down with one blast.  He had the granite earring on him and was the same faction as any other normal qeynos guard.  The problem with this guy is he thinks he is superman and attacks everything, "Halt, Halt, blah blah blah"  I think what makes this guy so rare is that he is killed pretty quickly after he spawns by common NK trash.  Best of luck to you all.</font></td></tr></table>
